{"tid":1467530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我當哂你地係屋企人！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:05:10.000Z","uid":291657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bef1b8a82077e869954c25e431a9220a2035ad","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"各位手足，哩段日子如果無左大家，我根本支持唔到，活唔到落去。係到好想多謝你地，但係更加重要嘅，係唔想大家互相指罵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然五大訴求得唔到回應，仲要一直有人被捕受傷，但係運動能夠持續到而家，全靠我地有共識，<strong>「不割蓆、不篤灰、不指責」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我地嘅抗爭模式一直都係「兄弟爬山，各有各位」，就算我地唔認同，<strong>都絕對唔會互相指罵</strong>。我地唔係口講民主，我地哩兩個幾月係真真正正實現緊民主！<br />\n<br />\n今晚連登嘅風氣真係好傷大家心，雖然可能好核突，但係<strong>我愛你地每一位手足</strong>。希望大家記住，其實我地無人知道點先係好，但係唔團結就一定無出路！<br />\n<br />\n應承我，有啲咩大家慢慢講，唔好再亂開post指責一齊共患難嘅手足，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割，大家係屋企人，割乜柒！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑暗過後，約哂你地除口罩係煲底見！唔好放我飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a36450eb135c76466b8ca6b08b53b9b3afa0bfa3","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"ec0e7665b8ac27526d2e91678c9278044cd69224","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"687dd73580d76c3b3e858fc77e04786e9f8e88d5","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72a3e97cbd01f9c5f4967f840fe25d77555daf12","tid":1467530,"uid":300323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"好多狗同三毛入黎帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都當晒大家一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔受傷唔被捕<br />\n一齊贏啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279049e6ee6496d79039d6399292e9b9f5ad1581","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a0d2653888c1fd6f22efc35cb4c5b5044cbf628","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30c04a2735951202ddad6526941b4cc72e05cebb","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"906d317816756ca6dd7543054f4b587c787a56c5","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c62662f8cda1a94155f4003c245f8fa8165e90a","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f657c1580888d75245ee2fe3a97d3d50639a5733","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0661b424864394a9ae0e107f6dc03526583fce4f","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:45.000Z","msg":"我愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7a1c2b9c2593510388c254d1cc70294d54344a","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbbefbae5c4f3f74ce7e6b809ea0dd4a0685e641","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"希望你地會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbf845f60df5c697462995ddc7d18b0374d32af","tid":1467530,"uid":291657,